ates","likelihood-mit-binomialverteilung","binomialverteilung-mit-r","globus-mit-9-treffern-bei-9-würfen","klausur-mit-20-richtig-falsch-fragen","münzwürfe-mit-3-treffern","unser-modell-ist-geboren","visualisierungen","zur-erinnerung-bayes-theorem","herleitung-bayes-theorem-12-gemeinsame-wahrscheinlichkeit","herleitung-bayes-theorem-22-posteriori-wahrscheinlichkeit","bayes-theorem-als-formel","posteriori-als-produkt-von-priori-und-likelihood","wissen-updaten-wir-füttern-daten-in-das-modell","bayes-berechnen-mit-mit-dem-bayes-gitter","idee","bayes-gitter-in-r-berechnen","was-sagt-die-post","aufgaben","abschluss","zusammenfassung","vertiefung","literatur"]}